<h1>SDL-Bullethell</h1>
<p>Project repo: <a href='https://github.com/nathan242/sdl-bullethell'>LINK</a></p>
<p>Compiled to WebAssembly: <a href='apps/bullethell/bullethell.html'>PLAY IN BROWSER</a> (You may have to click on the game to enable the sound)</p>

<h4>Introduction</h4>
<p>Bullethell space shooter game in C++ using SDL2.</p>
<p>The game has 3 levels each ending with a boss. Most of the games assets are AI generated (graphics/music/sfx).</p>
<p>This is built upon my own game engine which is based on code taken from my other SDL games.</p>

<img src='images/bullethell_1.png' style='border: 1px solid; border-color; #000000;' width='500' height='391'>
